Kau lompat.

150
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,480
Tidak bisa, kita lompat bersama.

151
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,680
Jangan bercanda, Xiaoyu.

152
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,760
Di sini tidak ada apa pun,
kita mau sembunyi ke mana?

153
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,760
Kau turun dulu.

154
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,360
Tidak bisa.

155
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,360
Lompat bersama saja.

156
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,040
Cepat.

157
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:17,880
Lin Nuoyan!

158
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,320
Xiaoyu.

159
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,170
Aku akan baik-baik saja.

160
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,720
Di depan jalan sana.

161
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,720
Aku hitung tiga dua satu, kau lompat.

162
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:28,890
Sudah dengar?

163
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,240
Bersiap.

164
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,240
Tiga.

165
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,200
Dua.

166
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:35,760
Satu.

167
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,320
Lompat!

168
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:00,640
Halo.

169
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,900
Kami dalam perjalanan kembali 
ke kota dari rumah duka.

170
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:06,360
